message.content:
I need to find the tax accrued but not yet paid from this balance sheet. This would be listed under the "Taxes Payable" line item, which represents tax obligations that have been recognized but not yet paid.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can see the "Taxes Payable" line item:

| Account | Initial_amount | Initial_date | End_amount | End_date |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Taxes Payable | 0.00 | 2023-12-31 | 253246.99 | 2024-01-29 |

The initial value as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00, meaning there were no unpaid tax obligations at the beginning of the period.

The end value as of 2024-01-29 is 253246.99, which represents the tax liability that has accrued but remains unpaid at the end of the period.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '253246.99'}}
```
